text: Country rap (also called country hip hop and sometimes hick hop) is a genre of music that combines compositions of hip hop with various forms of country music. ==Notable musicians== * Big Smo * Breland (musician) * Blanco Brown * Adam Calhoun * Lenny Cooper * Cowboy Troy * Ernest (musician) * Colt Ford * Georgia Florida Line * Jawga Boyz * Jelly Roll (singer) * Struggle Jennings * The Lacs * Lil Nas X * Moonshine Bandits * Kid Rock * Redneck Souljers * Bubba Sparxxx * Upchurch (musician) Category:Country music Category:Hip hop genres
title: Country rap
